                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9707" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0374</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1033 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智赋能，绿色引领：宝钢股份“双化”协同转型提升价值创造之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Empowered by Digital Intelligence,Led by Green: Baosteel&#39;s “Dualization” Synergistic Transformation to Enhance the Road of Value Creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">林红珍，李芳，程倩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宝山钢铁股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宝钢股份；“双化”协同转型；“六位一体”；价值创造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Baosteel; “Dualization” Synergistic Transformation; “Six-in-one”;Value Creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业作为传统的“三高”（高污染、高能耗、高排放）行业，长期以来一直是碳排放的“大户”，碳达峰、碳中和已经成为钢铁行业高质量发展的硬约束，数智化绿色化转型是钢铁行业实现可持续发展的必然选择。本案例聚焦宝钢股份数智化绿色化协同转型历程，描述其面临困境并克服转型挑战，产学研协同攻克行业“卡脖子”技术，积极实施数智化绿色化战略，从构建绿色采购系统、打造“智慧工厂”、以客户为中心建设智慧碳数据平台、实施废物处置绿色化及构建智慧管理系统，“六位一体”协同推进数智化绿色化转型，取得显著效果，入选 “灯塔工厂”、获“国家级绿色工厂”“数字领航示范企业”“双碳最佳实践能效标杆示范企业”等系列殊荣，成为引领传统“三高”企业“双化”协同转型的“灯塔”。本案例旨在引导学员了解“三高”企业数智化绿色化协同转型的动因、路径及措施和转型的效果，深入理解两大转型如何协同推动企业实现生产效率提升、成本降低、节能降碳、环境友好等多重目标，以及企业如何通过协同转型实现提升价值创造能力，引导学员深入理解数智化与绿色化转型的核心价值，掌握相关理论和方法，并将其融入日常管理工作中。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a traditional &quot;three high&quot; (high pollution, high energy consumption, and high emission) industry, the steel industry has long been a &quot;big player&quot; of carbon emissions, and carbon peak and carbon neutrality have become hard constraints on the high-quality development of the steel industry. The digital and intelligent green transformation is an inevitable choice for the steel industry to achieve sustainable development. This case focuses on the collaborative transformation process of digital intelligence and green transformation of Baosteel Co., Ltd., describes the difficulties it faces and overcomes the challenges of transformation, overcomes the industry&#39;s &quot;bottleneck&quot; technology through industry-university-research collaboration, and actively implements the digital and intelligent green strategy, from the construction of a green procurement system, the implementation of &quot;green and intelligent manufacturing, the construction of a customer-centric smart carbon data platform, the implementation of green waste disposal and the construction of a smart management system&quot;, the &quot;six-in-one&quot; collaborative promotion of digital and intelligent green transformation, and has achieved remarkable results, and has been selected as a &quot;lighthouse factory&quot; and a &quot;national green factory&quot; A series of awards such as &quot;Digital Pilot Demonstration Enterprise&quot; and &quot;Dual Carbon Best Practice Energy Efficiency Benchmarking Demonstration Enterprise&quot; have become a &quot;lighthouse&quot; leading the collaborative transformation of traditional &quot;three high&quot; enterprises. This case aims to guide students to understand the motivations, paths, measures and effects of the collaborative transformation of digital intelligence and green transformation of &quot;three high&quot; enterprises, and to deeply understand how the two transformations can synergistically promote enterprises to achieve multiple goals such as production efficiency improvement, cost reduction, energy conservation and carbon reduction, and environmental friendliness, as well as how enterprises can improve their value creation capabilities through collaborative transformation, and guide students to deeply understand the core values of digital intelligence and green transformation, master relevant theories and methods, and integrate them into daily management work.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“双化”协同转型；绿色动态能力；价值链理论；精益化管理；新质生产力</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-07</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
